OL,5,GA bit of common sense will benefit
OL,6,GVirgin Media customers from this week.
OL,8,FVirgin is reorganising its Electronic
OL,9,FProgramme Guide and is adopting one
OL,10,Fof Sky's best ideas.
OL,12,FA dedicated section is being created
OL,13,Ffor timeshift (i.e., plus one)
OL,14,Fchannels.
OL,16,FThis means these channels will be
OL,17,Fmuch easier to find as there will
OL,18,Falways be a clear link between the
OL,19,Fnumber of the main service and its
OL,20,Ftimeshift sibling. For instance, ITV
OL,21,F1 + 1 will be on 303 and Channel 4 +
OL,22,F1 will be on 304.
