OL,5,FIn turn, this frees up slots to
OL,6,Fpromote several channels up the list.
OL,8,FA few years ago, Sky did something
OL,9,Fsimilar. It cleared up the main
OL,10,Fsection of its EPG by creating
OL,11,Fdedicated sections for timeshift
OL,12,Fchannels and legacy SD services.
OL,14,FIt's all about simplicity and making
OL,15,Fnavigation as easy as possible for
OL,16,Fviewers.
OL,18,FSo Is it time to clear up the
OL,19,FFreeview EPG? It, frankly, is a mess.
