OL,5,FThis is all the more ironic as one of
OL,6,FFreeview's main selling points is
OL,7,Fthat it is the simple option for
OL,8,Fthose who may find technology
OL,9,Fconfusing.
OL,11,FThe main section of the Freeview EPG
OL,12,Fis a ragbag.
OL,14,FShopping channels and plus one
OL,15,Fchannels sit in random locations.
OL,17,FThe lower part of the guide is messed
OL,18,Fup by part-time "placeholder"
OL,19,Fchannels with very limited hours `
OL,20,Foften in the middle of the night.
